OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear for
OL,6,Fmany areas overnight, with a few fog
OL,7,Fpatches forming during the early
OL,8,Fhours. Thicker cloud across parts of
OL,9,FScotland may give the odd spot of
OL,10,Flight rain. Turning chilly, with a
OL,11,Frural frost.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAfter a chilly start, most
OL,14,Fwill have a warm and sunny day.
OL,15,FHowever, southern parts of Scotland
OL,16,Fand northern England will see more in
OL,17,Fthe way of cloud.
